<br>
What is ridiculous about Caen's Bo Staff?  Life taps don't draw aggro.<br>
<br>
Personally, I find the RZ sword ridiculous.  A warrior in my guild has one and puts out damn near the same damage I do when I use my Rune Etched Bamboo Bo and he is tanking the mob and I'm behind it.  Same ratio, but the damage bonus is much higher on the RZ weapon.  <br>
<br>
This warrior doesn't even have flurry maxed, nor critical hits maxed, nor PB maxed and he still out damages every monk in our guild except me and one other monk with a REBB.  All this from the front of the mob while the monks is on the rear.<br>
<br>
The 'monk damage' table is nothing more than slightly higher max damage for the same weapon damage compared to a warrior.  The end result is a warrior with decent offensive AA's can do monk damage with the RZ sword.<br>
<br>
Concerning taunt, I agree that warriors definitely need better taunt.  But concerning DPS, you guys are just fine unless you plan on lobbying for more monk and rogue DPS. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=494844" target="new">Rjey</a><br>
